OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill see scattered showers,
OL,7,Foccasionally heavy at first. Becoming
OL,8,Fmainly dry and cold overnight with
OL,9,Fsome frost. Still the odd shower along
OL,10,Fthe west coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FDry and frosty with sunny
OL,13,Fspells at first. Cloud will spread
OL,14,Fnorth but the afternoon will stay dry
OL,15,Fas the southerly wind strengthens.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
